ccre.saver

Class FakeStorageProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • ccre.saver.StorageProvider
      • ccre.saver.FakeStorageProvider

  • public class FakeStorageProvider
extends StorageProvider
    A fake storage provider that works, except that it doesn't save or load anything to disk. This is used if a proper provider cannot be found.
